         <div type="translation">
            <p>The bones of Marcus Perperna, freedman of Marcus, are buried here. Marcus Perperna Phila[  ], ivory polisher, (dedicated this).</p>
         </div>
         <div type="commentary">
            <p>Line 1 breaks off with an unclear letter, with a vertical stroke on the left being all that is preserved, possibly of an "N" or an "R".</p>
         </div>
